# KiwiSense V1 Bill of Materials

## Components

| Item | Quantity | Description |
|------|---------:|-------------|
| ESP32-WROOM-32 Development Board | 1 | Main microcontroller |
| Capacitive Soil Moisture Sensor | 1 | Measures soil moisture |
| DS18B20 Waterproof Temperature Sensor | 1 | Measures soil temperature |
| DHT22 Temperature & Humidity Sensor | 1 | Measures air conditions |
| 0.96" OLED Display (I²C) | 1 | Local display |
| 4.7kΩ Resistor | 1 | Pull-up resistor for DS18B20 |
| Breadboard | 1 | Prototype platform |
| Jumper Wires | Several | Electrical connections |
| USB Cable | 1 | ESP32 programming and power |

## Power Requirements

- Operating Voltage: **3.3V**
- USB Input: **5V via ESP32 USB**
- Estimated Current Consumption: **<200 mA**

## Version

KiwiSense V1
